rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;">  couple</a> of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/32142671.258409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL25ld3NsZXR0ZXJzLz=
IwMjAtMDUtMjgvbW9uZXktc3R1ZmYtd2lsbC10aGUtc2VjLWJ1c3QtZmFjZWJvb2stZm9yLWRyd=
