<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The standard view is that syndicated loans are=
 not securities, and a federal court agreed with JPMorgan and dismissed the=
 case.=C2=A0The investors appealed. The federal appeals court had the brigh=
t idea of asking the US Securities and Exchange Commission, which after all=
 regulates securities, for its views. The SEC is=C2=A0<em>very keenly inter=
ested </em>in the exact contours of what is and is not a security, so you m=
ight expect it to enthusiastically answer the court=E2=80=99s question. <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32142671.258409/aHR0c=
HM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMTgvc2VjLWRlY2xp=
