24a319a23cBb06e4ad3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">  But, nope</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Securities and Exchange Commission said it=
 is =E2=80=9Cnot in a position to file=E2=80=9D a brief giving its view on =
whether leveraged loans are securities, sidestepping a request to weigh in =
on a long-running lawsuit that may have major implications for the $1.4 tri=
llion market for risky debt.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A three-judge US Court of Appeals panel had so=
ught the SEC=E2=80=99s view on the question as it weighs a decision in a ca=
se that could upend the leveraged buyout machine and a decades-old market r=
iskier companies rely on for financing. The SEC=E2=80=99s filing had been h=
otly anticipated because the court was expected to lean heavily on its opin=
ion, legal experts earlier told Bloomberg.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDespite diligent efforts to respond t=
o the Court=E2=80=99s order and provide the Commission=E2=80=99s views, the=
 staff is unfortunately not in a position to file a brief on behalf of the =
Commission in this matter. We greatly appreciate the Court=E2=80=99s indulg=
ence and regret any inconvenience this may have caused the Court or the par=
ties,=E2=80=9D according to the letter filed on Tuesday and signed by SEC G=
eneral Counsel Megan Barbero.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The panel that=E2=80=99s deciding the case, Ki=
rschner v. JPMorgan, now will likely need to decide the case without input =
from the agency. If the court rules that the loan at the heart of the case =
was a security, it could usher sweeping new regulations into the market.</p=
>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ahahahaha what is going on here? I think it is=
 impossible to read this without reference to the SEC=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"=
https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32142671.258409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d=
3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMTMvdGhlLXNlYy1jcmFj=
