lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwNzIwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj=
1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb23d6f9c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  crackdown on cr=
yptocurrencies</a>. The SEC has been aggressive in asserting that <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32142671.258409/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDYtMDYvdGhlLXNlYy1j=
b21lcy1mb3ItY3J5cHRvP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA3MjAyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1=
haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDcyMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW=
