scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  virtually all cry=
pto tokens are securities</a> and subject to SEC regulation, but=C2=A0that =
position has gotten a lot of criticism from the crypto industry and some po=
liticians. And last week the SEC had a strange but important loss in court,=
 when <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32142671.258=
409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMTQ=
vcmlwcGxlLWlzLWEtc2VjdXJpdHktYW5kLWl0LWlzbi10P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA3MjAyM19NT05FWV=
NUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzM=
DcyMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB81fd43ef" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"col=
or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">  a federal district court</a> ruled that Ripple=E2=80=99s XRP token =
sometimes is and sometimes isn=E2=80=99t a security.<a class=3D"footnote-in=
dex" href=3D"#footnote-2" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
