<span>[2]</span>
</a>=C2=A0The SEC will presumably appeal that decision. There is a live=C2=
=A0controversy over what securities laws apply to crypto, and the SEC is pu=
shing a maximal approach.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mostly that approach consists of litigating cr=
ypto cases, but the SEC tries to stay on-message generally. We <a href=3D"h=
ttps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32142671.258409/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3=
cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMTMvY2Vsc2l1cy13YXMtb=
